TITLE: Implementing State Management in JavaScript using Dapr SDK
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code demonstrating state management operations using Dapr's client SDK to save, retrieve and delete state from a state store.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/getting-started/quickstarts/statemanagement-quickstart.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const client = new DaprClient()

// Save state into a state store
await client.state.save(DAPR_STATE_STORE_NAME, order)
console.log("Saving Order: ", order)

// Get state from a state store
const savedOrder = await client.state.get(DAPR_STATE_STORE_NAME, order.orderId)
console.log("Getting Order: ", savedOrder)

// Delete state from the state store
await client.state.delete(DAPR_STATE_STORE_NAME, order.orderId)
console.log("Deleting Order: ", order)
```

