TITLE: Implementing Default and Named Resiliency Policies in Dapr
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet demonstrates how to configure both default and named resiliency policies for various targets in a Dapr solution. It includes global policies, component-specific policies, and named policies that are applied to specific applications, actors, and components.
