TITLE: Implementing Dapr Workflow in Go
DESCRIPTION: This Go code implements a Dapr workflow for processing orders. It includes workflow and activity registration, inventory management, and workflow execution. The main function sets up the workflow, processes an order, and waits for completion.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/getting-started/quickstarts/workflow-quickstart.md#2025-04-21_snippet_27

