TITLE: Defining Resiliency Policies in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML configuration defines retry and circuit breaker policies for the 'order-processor' application and 'statestore' component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/getting-started/quickstarts/resiliency/resiliency-state-quickstart.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
apiVersion: dapr.io/v1alpha1
kind: Resiliency
metadata:
  name: myresiliency
scopes:
  - checkout

spec:
  policies:
    retries:
      retryForever:
        policy: constant
        maxInterval: 5s
        maxRetries: -1 

    circuitBreakers:
      simpleCB:
        maxRequests: 1
        timeout: 5s 
        trip: consecutiveFailures >= 5

  targets:
    apps:
      order-processor:
        retry: retryForever
        circuitBreaker: simpleCB
```

