TITLE: Returning ETag Mismatch Error in Java
DESCRIPTION: This Java code demonstrates how to return an ETag Mismatch error in a Dapr pluggable component using Project Reactor. It creates a Status object with a FAILED_PRECONDITION code and includes a BadRequest.FieldViolation detail.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/developing-applications/develop-components/pluggable-components/develop-pluggable.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

