SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/operations/configuration/configuration-overview.md#2025-04-21_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
apiVersion: dapr.io/v1alpha1
kind: Configuration
metadata:
  name: myappconfig
spec: 
  components:
    deny:
      - bindings.smtp
      - secretstores.local.file
```

