TITLE: Publishing Raw Messages in PHP with Dapr Client
DESCRIPTION: Example using Dapr PHP SDK to publish a raw message to a topic without CloudEvent encapsulation by setting the rawPayload metadata to true.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/developing-applications/building-blocks/pubsub/pubsub-raw.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

require_once __DIR__.'/vendor/autoload.php';

$app = \Dapr\App::create();
$app->run(function(\DI\FactoryInterface $factory) {
    $publisher = $factory->make(\Dapr\PubSub\Publish::class, ['pubsub' => 'pubsub']);
    $publisher->topic('TOPIC_A')->publish('data', ['rawPayload' => 'true']);
});
```

