DESCRIPTION: This YAML configuration disables the state v1.0 HTTP API while allowing all other HTTP APIs. It demonstrates using a denylist in the Dapr Configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/operations/configuration/api-allowlist.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
apiVersion: dapr.io/v1alpha1
kind: Configuration
metadata:
  name: myappconfig
  namespace: default
spec:
  api:
    denied:
      - name: state
        version: v1.0
        protocol: http
```

