TITLE: Configuring Circuit Breaker Policy in Dapr YAML
DESCRIPTION: Example YAML configuration for a circuit breaker policy named 'pubsubCB'. This configuration sets the maximum requests to 1, interval to 8 seconds, timeout to 45 seconds, and trips when consecutive failures exceed 8.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/operations/resiliency/policies/circuit-breakers.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
spec:
  policies:
    circuitBreakers:
      pubsubCB:
        maxRequests: 1
        interval: 8s
        timeout: 45s
        trip: consecutiveFailures > 8
```

