TITLE: Retrieving Configuration Items Using Dapr .NET SDK
DESCRIPTION: C# example showing how to retrieve configuration items from a Dapr configuration store. It uses the Dapr client to get the values of 'orderId1' and 'orderId2' from the 'configstore' component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/developing-applications/building-blocks/configuration/howto-manage-configuration.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
