SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/developing-applications/building-blocks/actors/actor-reentrancy.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { CommunicationProtocolEnum, DaprClient, DaprServer } from "@dapr/dapr";

// Configure the actor runtime with the DaprClientOptions.
const clientOptions = {
  actor: {
    reentrancy: {
      enabled: true,
      maxStackDepth: 32,
    },
  },
};
```

