SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/operations/observability/tracing/setup-tracing.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
apiVersion: dapr.io/v1alpha1
kind: Configuration
metadata:
  name: tracing
spec:
  tracing:
    samplingRate: "1"
    otel:
      endpointAddress: "localhost:4317"
      isSecure: false
      protocol: grpc 
```

