string randomString = GetRandomString();
```

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
// DON'T DO THIS!
Instant currentTime = Instant.now();
UUID newIdentifier = UUID.randomUUID();
String randomString = getRandomString();
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// DON'T DO THIS!
const currentTime = new Date();
const newIdentifier = uuidv4();
