TITLE: JavaScript Workflow Activity Context Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implements the WorkflowActivityContext class in TypeScript/JavaScript that provides core workflow activity functionality including instance and activity ID management.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/developing-applications/building-blocks/workflow/howto-author-workflow.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default class WorkflowActivityContext {
  private readonly _innerContext: ActivityContext;
  constructor(innerContext: ActivityContext) {
    if (!innerContext) {
      throw new Error("ActivityContext cannot be undefined");
    }
    this._innerContext = innerContext;
  }

  public getWorkflowInstanceId(): string {
    return this._innerContext.orchestrationId;
  }

  public getWorkflowActivityId(): number {
    return this._innerContext.taskId;
  }
}
```

