TITLE: Downloading Worker Code Using cURL
DESCRIPTION: Shell command for downloading the pre-compiled Worker code from the Dapr GitHub repository.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dapr/docs/blob/v1.15/daprdocs/content/en/reference/components-reference/supported-bindings/cloudflare-queues.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
# Set this to the version of Dapr that you're using
DAPR_VERSION="release-1.12"
curl -LfO "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dapr/components-contrib/${DAPR_VERSION}/internal/component/cloudflare/workers/code/worker.js"
```

